---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Lord Ben's art cave";
import banner from '../assets/art/sketches/site/banner.png';
---
<BaseLayout>
  <img 
    src={banner} 
    alt="Banner"
    style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px; margin: 1rem 0;"
  >
  <h2>Welcome</h2>
  <p>Greetings! I'm glad that you found this page. <br> Here you may read what I am thinking about, my opinions on technology and, maybe even my art. (at some point in the future)</p>
  <p>If you want to know whats going on in my head, your best chance of finding out are my <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}blog/`}>blog posts</a>, where I write about pretty much anything I feel like writing about. </p>
</BaseLayout>